Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Mexico strikes oil
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b040bxlj
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 11 Mar 1979
US eyes vast new oil finds in Mexico. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014.